room_title: Escape room "Missing Attorney" by Ruse Escape Room in Fort Collins
room_description: Our friend, who is a local attorney, has gone missing. You have been called in to help us find the clues he left behind in his office. Did he get kidnapped? Is he hiding out? Or did something else happen? You have one hour to find the clues he left or you will face being arrested for tampering with evidence.
